This package contains C libraries and utilities for building ToolBus client
applications.

See 
  http://www.cwi.nl/projects/metaEnv/toolbus 

for information about the ToolBus coordination architecture.


Installations
=============

1) Run ./reconf
2) Run ./configure --prefix=installation-prefix
3) Run make
4) Run make install


Compatibility
=============
Note that this version of toolbuslib is intended for usage with the Next Generation ToolBus.
This renders this version incompatible with the C implementation of the ToolBus.
The latest revision that is compatible with the C implementation of the ToolBus is 21994.
 